Dino Melaye is a former senator from Nigeria who served as the senator representing Kogi West in the 8th Nigerian National Assembly.
Peter Obi is wonderful and a good man, but he is unable to unite Nigerians, the author wrote in a post on his official Instagram account. More significant than reducing the expense of governing is unity.
In a video he shared, he discussed his friendship with Peter Obi and the current needs of Nigerians.
His hometown is Ayetoro Gbede, which is in Kogi State’s Ijumu Local Government Area.
he was sharing the post on his verified Facebook page account with over one million potential followers for the enjoyment of viewers, he said below.
“Peter obi is fantastic and a good man but he lacks capacity to unify Nigerians. Unity more important than cutting cost of governance”
As expected, a few minutes ago, after the post surfaced online, his fans and followers reacted in the comments box section from a variety of ways.
